headline: American Beacon Partners Names John Linnehan Chief Financial Officer
summary: IRVING, Texas, February 19, 2026--John Linnehan joins American Beacon Partners as CFO, overseeing American Beacon’s financial health, strategic planning, and corporate initiatives.
